title: Hour 1 - Kevin Durant Still Wants a Trade, Aaron Judge Goes Deep Again
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Kevin Durant Still Wants a Trade, Aaron Judge Goes Deep Again
description:
Dan talks about the Brooklyn Nets reaction to Kevin Durant's continued demands, and he acknowledges Yankees slugger Aaron Judge's greatness after he knocks his 44th HR of the season.
